d distinguish us from our peers the journey began over  years ago and continues today consol energy strives each and every day to maintain its position as an innovator and one of the safest and most respected energy producers in the world about us company stats our history corporate governance board of directors management news  consol ceo trump administration wants to be facilitator for tristate energy industry read more   new study projects  million more natural gas related jobs by  read more  view all    investors media land resources job seekers     about us land resources investor relations newsroom contact us operations responsibility careers privacy policy   consol energy inc  all rights reserved consol energy  newsroom newsroom contact us loading data step  of  search for       home about us company stats our history corporate governance board of directors management operations exploration and production midstream cnx coal resources lp convey water systems llc marine terminal doing business with consol what it takes to do business with consol supplier diversity land resources royalty and other payments request to use consol surface properties rental homes tax authorities forms contact us responsibility message from the ceo core values safety environment corporate responsibility reports investor relations stock information interactive chart dividends analysts coverage news releases financials annual reports sec filings events and presentations events presentations investor resources transfer agent and registrar risk factors email alerts contact us careers career search newsroom   investors investors consol energy announces filing of form  registration statement for spinoff of its pennsylvania mining operations and other coal assets second quarter  earnings release and call schedule learn more ► responsibility responsibility from the safety of our employees to the environment and communities in which we work and live consol energy’s corporate responsibility ef