cumberland coal trade production  consol energy was originally created in  as the consolidation coal company after several small mining companies in western maryland decided to combine their operations the company was formally established in  and headquartered in cumberland maryland for the first  years – where the company became the largest bituminous coal company in the eastern united states western marylands coal production rose about  million short tons in  exceeded  million short tons by the turn of the century and reached an alltime high of about  million short tons in  a small amount of the coal production in the early s was premium smithing coal as in blacksmith that was specially processed and delivered in boxcars to customers throughout the united states and canada in  consolidation coal company was merged with pittsburgh coal company and its headquarters were moved to western pennsylvania  with growing demand for natural gas in the us following world war ii consolidation coal company was acquired by the continental oil company or conoco in  by the mids consolidation coal company operated  mines and employed nearly  miners in  conoco along with consolidation coal company was acquired by dupont which then sold some of its coal mining interests in pennsylvania to the german energy company rheinbraun ag consol energy presentedit looking to invest in coal reserves in north america rheinbraun ag offered dupont stakes in coal mines and  million in  to join in an equal part joint venture creating consol energy despite the cost of coal dropping in the s consols longterm contracts and investments in longwall mining techniques allowed the company to remain competitive in  dupont sold the large majority of its stake in consol leaving it with only a  percent share and rheinbraun ag with a  percent interest consol also acquired rochester  pittsburgh coal company in  in  consol underwent a public offering nyse cnx in order to pay down some of the debt the company had incurred with the majority buyout from dupont and the acquisition of rochester  pittsburgh coal company due to uncertainty surrounding demand for coal in the early s consol began to place a greater emphasis on diversification primarily into natural gas consols first major natural gas investment was through the acquisition of mcn energy group incs methane reserves in southwestern virginia for  million in  consol acquired conoco incs coalbed methane gas production assets in southwestern virginia consol subsidiaries cnx ventures and cnx land resources also began diversification efforts during this time into methane gas and timber and farming in  consol spun off its subsidiary cnx gas as a standalone company but retained  percent of the new companys shares on june  consol energy entered the sp  replacing knightridder in  cnx gas also began investing heavily in natural gas exploration in the marcellus shale in pennsylvania in  consol acquired dominion resources incs natural gas production and exploration assets for  billion dollars which included nearly  acres of marcellus potential tripling consols position in the marcellus to approximately  acres consol also acquired all of the remaining publicly owned shares of cnx gas for a cash payment of  million in  consol was also named by forbes magazine as one of the  most trustworthy companies in  consol entered into two separate joint venture agreements to expedite its natural gas production the first an agreement with noble energy inc will jointly develop the companys  marcellus shale acres in pennsylvania and west virginia the second joint agreement with hess corporation will jointly explore and develop consols nearly  utica shale acres in ohio consol also began an expansion of its baltimore terminal in  to increase capacity from  million to  million tons to increase its revenue from sales of its metallurgical coal operations and financialsedit divisions and areas of businessedit consol energy operates as a producer of multip