ecil township pennsylvania us key people j brett harvey chairman david m khani cfo  executive vp nicholas j deiuliis president  ceo stephen w johnson chief administrative officer  executive vp products coal natural gas timber electric power services transportation revenue us billion   number of employees  website wwwconsolenergycom consol energy inc kənˈsɒl is an american energy company with interests in coal and natural gas production headquartered in the suburb of cecil township in the southpointe complex just outside pittsburgh pennsylvania in april  consol energy had divested all of its coal operations except for the pennsylvania mine which it was in the process of spinning off into an independent company in  consol was the leading producer of highbtu bituminous coal in the united states and the uss largest underground coal mining company the company has natural gas reserves totaling  trillion cu ft as of  and employs more than  people contents  history  consolidation coal company –  consol energy present  operations and financials  divisions and areas of business  financials  corporate responsibility  environmental record  political involvement  naming rights  see also  references  further reading  external links historyedit consolidation coal company –edit table of cumberland coal trade production  consol energy was originally created in  as the consolidation coal company after several small mining companies in western maryland decided to combine their operations the company was formally established in  and headquartered in cumberland maryland for the first  years – where the company became the largest bituminous coal company in the eastern united states western marylands coal production rose about  million short tons in  exceeded  million short tons by the turn of the century and reached an alltime high of about  million short tons in  a small amount of the coal production in the early s was premium smithing coal as in blacksmith that was specially processed and delivered in boxcars to customers throughout the united states and canada in  consolidation coal company was merged with pittsburgh coal company and its headquarters were moved to western pennsylvania  with growing demand for natural gas in the us following world war ii consolidation coal company was acquired by the continental oil company or conoco in  by the mids consolidation coal company operated  mines and employed nearly  miners in  conoco along with consolidation coal company was acquired by dupont which then sold some of its coal mining interests in pennsylvania to the german energy company rheinbraun ag consol energy presentedit looking to invest in coal reserves in north america rheinbraun ag offered dupont stakes in coal mines and  million in  to join in an equal part joint venture creating consol energy despite the cost of coal dropping in the s consols longterm contracts and investments in longwall mining techniques allowed the company to remain competitive in  dupont sold the large majority of its stake in consol leaving it with only a  percent share and rheinbraun ag with a  percent interest consol also acquired rochester  pittsburgh coal company in  in  consol underwent a public offering nyse cnx in order to pay down some of the debt the company had incurred with the majority buyout from dupont and the acquisition of rochester  pittsburgh coal company due to uncertainty surrounding demand for coal in the early s consol began to place a greater emphasis on diversification primarily into natural gas consols first major natural gas investment was through the acquisition of mcn energy group incs methane reserves in southwestern virginia for  million in  consol acquired conoco incs coalbed methane gas production assets in southwestern virginia consol subsidiaries cnx ventures and cnx land resources also began diversification efforts during this time into methane gas and timber and farming in  consol spun off its subsidiary cnx gas as a standalone company but retained  percent of the new companys shares on june  consol energy entered the sp  replacing knightridder in  cnx gas also began investing heavily in natural gas exploration in the marcellus shale in pennsylvania in  consol acquired dominion resources incs natural gas production and exploration assets for  billion dollars which included nearly  acres of marcellus potential tripling consols position in the marcellus to approximately  acres consol also acquired all of the remaining publicly owned shares of cnx gas for a cash payment of  million in  consol was also named by forbes magazine as one of the  most trustworthy companies in  consol entered into two separate joint venture agreements to expedite its natural gas production the first an agreement with noble energy inc will jointly develop the companys  marcellus shale acres in pennsylvania and west virginia the second joint agreement with hess corporation will jointly explore and develop consols nearly  utica shale acres in ohio consol also began an expansion of its baltimore terminal in  to increase capacity from  million to  million tons to increase its revenue from sales of its metallurgical coal operations and financialsedit divisions and areas of businessedit consol energy operates as a producer of multiple energy sources primarily for electric power generation the companys largest assets consist of its coal and natural gas divisions but consol also maintains support services including baltimore marine terminal river division research  development land division and fairmont supply company consols coal division operates  coal mining complexes in four states in the united states including pennsylvania west virginia virginia and utah as of  the company maintained an estimated  billion tons of proven and probable coal reserves and produced nearly  million tons of coal in  the coal produced from these mining operations are sold from offices in pittsburgh pa philadelphia pa and atlanta ga consols coal division received the us department of the interiors office of surface mining national award for excellence in surface mining for the companys innovative reclamation practices in   and  consols gas division deals with natural gas exploration development and production producing nearly  billion cubic feet of coalbed methane in  with the acquisition of the exploration and production business of dominion resources in  the company has access to over  trillion cubic feet of proved cleanburning natural gas reserves in pennsylvania west virginia and ohio including coalbed methane and shale beds the company currently has nearly  net producing wells as the owner of more than  surface acres in the us and canada consol energy has a land division that oversees various projects including selling reserve land that the company does not develop land donation and conservation projects consol energy has also been recognized for its reclamation efforts by national and state governments and has worked in partnership with several conservation groups on land reclamation projects consols river division oversees transportation of coal and other products on the monongahela allegheny kanawha and ohio rivers with  tow and tugboats and over  barges consols baltimore marine terminal provides coal transshipment services from rail cars to ocean transport ships consols water division is involved in water purification with a focus on treating wastewater produced as a byproduct of hydraulic fracturing the company operates reverse osmosis water purification plants and has a minority interest in a company that develops solarpowered water purification systems which as of july update was conducting a pilot test at one of consols gas drilling sites consol also maintains the fairmont supply company dedicated to the sale and distribution of mining services and equipment additionally the company operates the largest privately owned research and development facility in the industry that is devoted exclusively to coal and energy utilization and production financialsedit in  consol energy had an annual revenue of  billion customers primarily include electric utilities and steel mills in the us but demand from european utilities has increased during the s consol energy was ranked number  on the fortune  list in  corporate responsibilityedit boat operated by consol energy passing downtown pittsburgh pa environmental recordedit in september  several thousand fish were killed in dunkard creek monongalia county west virginia while state officials attributed the fish kill to a golden algae bloom an investigation by the environmental protection agency claimed that mining discharges from consol energys blacksville no  mine created the conditions for the golden algae bloom after halting operations at the mine following the fish kill consol was allowed to continue mining operations after coming to an agreement with the west virginia department of environmental protection to submit a proposal for discharge treatment plants by april  of  consol also invested  million in a water treatment facility and paid a  million federal penalty to the us department of justice and half to the west virginia department of environmental protection in  the company maintains that it was never found liable for the fish kill as a producer of coal and natural gas the environmental impact of coal mining and natural gas drilling has been a subject of controversy for consol energy despite this the company has been recognized for its efforts at environmental protection and was awarded the us environmental protection agency climate protection award in  additionally consol maintains ongoing environmental efforts aimed at restoring and enhancing property managed by the company and has worked with conservation groups including ducks unlimited and the national wild turkey federation on habitat restoration efforts political involvementedit an ad by the national rifle association critical of president barack obama that was filmed on consols blacksville no  coal mine in west virginia became an issue of political debate in  the national rifle association intended to ask miners the question how do you feel about having your second amendment rights taken away if obama becomes president word spread among proobama miners who contacted their union the united mine workers of america resulting in  miners taking the day off to avoid appearing in the ad in a contractsanctioned protest halting production at consols blacksville no  coal mine lobbying efforts on the part of consol have also been an issue of controversy in the first quarter of  consol spent  million in lobbying expenses on issues relating to the coal mining and natural gas industries naming rightsedit consol energy has put its name to two sports facilities in its pittsburgharea in  consol energy purchased the naming rights to washington pennsylvanias minor league baseball team the washington wild things field consol energy park consol later purchased the naming rights to the consol energy center in  the arena that hosts the pittsburgh penguins national hockey league team  it is estimated that consol energy won the bid for naming rights at a cost between    million per year for  years as of october  the consol energy center has been renamed ppg paints arena as consol energy has ended its naming rights of the venue  see alsoedit pittsburgh portal energy portal companies portal cumberland and pennsylvania railroad consol energy mine map preservation project referencesedit  american water works set to join the sp  consol energy to join sp midcap   retrieved    consol energy governance consol energy  retrieved    a b about us  consol energy consol energy  retrieved august     consol energy inc hoovers retrieved    httpwwwslatecomarticleshealthandscienceclimatedeskpruittscoalmineisownedbypeoplewhowanttogetoutofcoalmininghtml  a b c d e f g  k consol energy consol energy inc retrieved    a b c consol energy inc funding universe retri